Package: cytokineFindeR
Type: Package
Title: Measure and rank ligands of interest (cytokines) across different methods and databases
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jeffrey", family = "Tang", email = "jeffrey.tang@hli.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5633-6123")),
             person(given = "Amrit", family = "Singh", email = "amrit.singh@hli.ubc.ca", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7475-1646")))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for measuring and analyzing cytokines and 
    other ligands of interest across a handful of statistical methods and biological 
    databases using ligand-receptor interactions (LRIs). Provides functions for data retrieval,
    statistical analysis, and visualization of cytokine expression patterns using pre-defined 
    receptor gene sets.
